data.description: THIS IS IT! Come see this lovely home which has one of the largest square footages in the area. The floor plan boasts 4 bedrooms, 2 baths, a home office, and a large pantry/laundry room. It also features a detached studio for extra rental income potential. Updated kitchen with granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and double oven. Oversized primary suite that comes with a walk-in closet and its own private entrance. Large patio area has potential to be turned into a nice space for true outdoor entertaining and living. Parking for Boat, RV or several vehicles. Minutes to I-95, and the famous Las Olas Boulevard. 10 minutes from Downtown Fort Lauderdal's Art and Entertainment District. 15 minutes from one of the most beautiful beaches in Florida.
